<section class="faq-section py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
      <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="faq-subtitle">Everything you need to know before your treatment</p>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion faq-accordion" id="faqAccordion">

      <!-- Prepare for massage -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
          <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">
            How should I prepare for a massage?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <ul>
              <li>Please double-check your address and confirm you have booked the correct treatment.</li>
              <li>Ensure there is enough space for a massage table (approximately 2m x 3m) with room to move around.</li>
              <li>Choose a comfortable room that is easy to access and warm enough for treatment.</li>
              <li>Prepare two large towels and one small towel for the headrest.</li>
              <li>If possible, take a shower beforehand to help relax the muscles.</li>
              <li>You may also wish to mention any health conditions, allergies, parking instructions, or building access details before the appointment.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- During appointment -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">
            What happens during my appointment?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <ul>
              <li>I will ask where you would like the massage table set up.</li>
              <li>You will be given complete privacy to get comfortable before the session begins.</li>
              <li>All treatments are strictly professional and non-sexual.</li>
              <li>Underwear should remain on throughout the session.</li>
              <li>I operate a zero-tolerance policy toward inappropriate behaviour.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Treatment time -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">
            Does treatment time include set-up and pack-down?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Your booking time includes the full session from set-up to pack-down.</p>

            <p>For example, during a 60-minute appointment:</p>

            <ul>
              <li><strong>First 5-10 minutes:</strong> consultation, hygiene preparation, and table set-up.</li>
              <li><strong>Main session:</strong> hands-on treatment.</li>
              <li><strong>Final 5-10 minutes:</strong> aftercare advice, cleaning, and equipment pack-down.</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Occasionally you may receive slightly more hands-on time depending on the schedule that day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour">
            What should I do after my treatment?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">

            <p>It is normal to feel slightly sore after a deep tissue or sports massage. This should settle within a few days.</p>

            <strong>Sports & Deep Tissue Massage</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>Allow your body time to rest.</li>
              <li>Avoid intense exercise for the rest of the day.</li>
              <li>Continue with any stretches that were recommended.</li>
              <li>Heat or ice may help if soreness occurs.</li>
            </ul>

            <strong>Relaxation Treatments</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>Drink plenty of water.</li>
              <li>Avoid alcohol and caffeine for a few hours.</li>
              <li>Allow time to relax afterwards.</li>
            </ul>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Qualifications -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive">
            What qualifications does Tom have?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Tom holds a degree in Sports Therapy from the University of Bath, along with a Premier BTEC Level 5 Professional Diploma in Soft Tissue Therapy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Arrival -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix">
            When will Tom arrive?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>I aim to arrive at your scheduled booking time and may occasionally arrive a few minutes early to prepare the treatment area.</p>
            <p>If there are any travel delays, I will contact you as soon as possible and keep you updated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Late -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSeven">
            What if I’m running late?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>If you are running late, please contact Tom as soon as possible.</p>
            <p>Your session may need to be shortened if another appointment is scheduled afterwards.</p>
            <p>If you are unable to attend, please cancel your booking to avoid waiting time and disruption to other clients.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!--opening times -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqEight">
            What are your opening hours?
          </button>
        </h2>

        <div id="faqEight" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>I offer appointments Monday to Friday, between 10:00am and 10:00pm.</p>
            <p>Evening appointments are available, but I recommend booking in advance as these are the most popular times.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Coverage -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNine">
            What areas do you cover?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Tom is based in South London and covers:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>South London</li>
              <li>Surrey – Guildford, Farnborough, Woking, Reigate, Banstead and Tandridge</li>
              <li>Berkshire – Slough, Windsor and Maidenhead</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you are outside these areas, please contact Tom with your address and a travel quote can be provided.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
